#: src/components/docs/publishing-docs-page.tsx
msgid "Whether tapping an article opens it inline in Standard Reader, or takes the reader straight to your site, depends on one thing: does the record's <0>content</0> field hold a body in a format Standard Reader knows how to render? If <1>content</1> is missing, or set to a format we don't recognize, the article is treated as an external post and always opens on your site — even if <2>textContent</2> carries a plain-text excerpt. To get inline reading, publish the article body in <3>content</3> using one of the recognized formats below."
msgstr "点击一篇文章后，是在 Standard Reader 内直接打开，还是直接跳转到你的站点，取决于一点：记录的 <0>content</0> 字段中是否包含 Standard Reader 能够渲染的格式的正文？如果 <1>content</1> 缺失，或使用了我们无法识别的格式，该文章会被视为外部帖子，并始终在你的站点上打开——即使 <2>textContent</2> 中带有纯文本摘要。若想实现内嵌阅读，请使用下列受支持格式之一，将文章正文发布在 <3>content</3> 中。"

